'''Willis Wode''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. He is played by guest star [[Ryan McKenna]] and debuts in &quot;[[Cripples, Bastards and Broken Things]].&quot; Ser Willis Wode is a [[Knighthood|knight]] in the service of [[House Whent]]. He helps [[Catelyn Stark]] to apprehend [[Tyrion Lannister]] and dies defending her during her passage through [[the Vale of Arryn]].

